    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189680/extras/38c8db395eff02a4e39f05386680223c.avif?t=1744223658\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189680/extras_big/38c8db395eff02a4e39f05386680223c.avif?t=1744223658 width=800 height=102 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到《Dungeon CEO》的混乱世界，在这里开启你的新维多利亚风格地牢经营之旅。作为地牢公司新上任的首席执行官，你的当务之急是摆脱公司长久以来拖欠的债务。你的任务是什么？让你的怪物劳动力活下去，有效管理资源，尽可能多地赚取金币，同时在利润和危险之间取得微妙的平衡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189680/extras/da6caa0f8be902e073bd91b98b47496c.poster.avif?t=1744223658\" width=798 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189680/extras/da6caa0f8be902e073bd91b98b47496c.webm?t=1744223658\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189680/extras/da6caa0f8be902e073bd91b98b47496c.mp4?t=1744223658\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款角色扮演策略卡牌游戏中，每一个决定都至关重要。雇佣最优秀的人员，组建强大的卡组，为艰苦的回合制战斗做好准备。卡组中的每一张牌都能通过指挥和提升你的部队改变战局，让你智取并战胜对手。击败敌人赚取现金，壮大您的地下城帝国，将地下城公司推向辉煌的顶峰。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是要将公司推向新的高峰，还是要跌入潜伏的动荡之中？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189680/extras/a9e26a7032468cc87a532c7f0bac8ef5.poster.avif?t=1744223658\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189680/extras/a9e26a7032468cc87a532c7f0bac8ef5.webm?t=1744223658\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189680/extras/a9e26a7032468cc87a532c7f0bac8ef5.mp4?t=1744223658\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>**注：本游戏为免费试玩版。开发团队需要支持和反馈以继续开发。</i></strong></p>",
